Project on heroku - https://hit-pizza.herokuapp.com/

SET UP LOCALLY:
node v12.12.0
npm v6.11.3
@angular/cli v~9.1.4

install angular cli global
npm i @angular/cli -g

start frontend
cd client
npm install
npm run start

start backend
from root
npm install
npm start


